│ the inactive lane. The widened load is emitted unmasked (wide.load). In LLVM  │
│ IR semantics, loading from a poison pointer operand is immediate UB,          │
│ regardless of memory safety. The original scalar loop never executed those    │
│ instructions for iv=9. Thus the transformation makes the program less         │
│ defined: the source is defined, target triggers UB. Alive2 confirms this:     │
