│ i64>, ptr %10, align 1\nThe load is unconditional and unmasked. Only the      │
│ stores are predicated. No mask guards the load, so lane 0's poison-derived    │
│ pointer is dereferenced. The legality/cost model decided no mask was required │
│ for this load (Legal->isMaskRequired(load)==false) and treated it as safe to  │
